body: You just need to rename the created txt file from retraining and paste it in the assets directory, the created txt file is not the same name as the default txt file, if so will result to incorrect output, both files "created.txt and default.txt" should be on the same directory on android build and the LABEL_FILE should be pointing to created txt file from retraining you renamed.
